<chapter xml:id="chapter-DOTF" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Derivatives of Transcendental Functions</title>
        <introduction>
            <p>
                Transcendental functions include trigonometric functions, exponential functions, and logarithmic functions. Also, more advanced functions, including inverse trigonometric functions, hyperbolic trigonometric functions, and inverse hyperbolic functions.
            </p>
        </introduction>

